  <main class="container">
    <section id="about" aria-labelledby="about-title">
      <h2 id="about-title">About The Indian Conclave (TIC)</h2>
      <p>
        The Indian Conclave (TIC) is one of the most prestigious Model United Nations conferences in India, dedicated to fostering diplomacy, leadership, and global awareness among youth. 
        Since its inception, TIC has been a platform where students from diverse backgrounds come together to simulate the workings of the United Nations, debate pressing international issues, and develop critical skills such as negotiation, public speaking, and research.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our conference emphasizes inclusivity, intellectual rigor, and cultural exchange. Delegates engage in committees ranging from Security Council to specialized agencies, tackling real-world challenges like climate change, human rights, and global security. 
        TIC is committed to creating an environment that nurtures future leaders who are empathetic, informed, and ready to make a positive impact on the world stage.
      </p>
      <p>
        Beyond debate, TIC offers workshops, guest lectures by diplomats and experts, and networking opportunities that enrich the delegate experience. Join us to be part of a transformative journey that sharpens your skills and broadens your worldview.
      </p>
    </section>

